# bind -P/p: dump-functions  (bind -p|\grep -v '^#'|\grep -v 'self-insert')
# bind -S/s: dump-macros
# bind -V/v: dump-variables

C-hjkl to move between words like C-arrows (h/j=up/down in history)
M-hl to move left/right charwise like in vim
C-b like backspace

C-x C-s add parameters to the last command
C-x C-x quote params

      +-------------+
      | WORD | word |
+-----+-------------+
|Left | C-w  | C-d  |
|-----+-------------+
|Right| M-w  | M-d  |
+-----+-------------+
